<task id="task_m5t_sf1_pvb">
    <title>Getting the Standalone Agent's Installer Package</title>
    <taskbody>
        <context id="context_kgv_tyg_pvb">
            <p>For standalone agents, follow instructions below to get the agent's installer
                package.</p>
        </context>
        <steps>
            <step>
                <cmd>Go to our <xref
                        href="https://www.trendmicro.com/en_us/business/products/downloads.html"
                        format="html" scope="external">Software Download Center</xref>.</cmd>
            </step>
            <step>
                <cmd>Find
                        <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="153,255,255"?><uicontrol>StellarProtect</uicontrol><?oxy_custom_end?>
                    and click it. You will be directed to the web page with the latest firmware
                    version for StellarProtect.</cmd>
            </step>
            <step>
                <cmd>Be sure you are on the <uicontrol>Product Download/Update</uicontrol> tab
                    page.</cmd>
            </step>
            <step>
                <cmd>Find the file name starting with <filepath>txsp-</filepath> and click it to
                    download the
                        <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="153,255,255"?><ph
                        conkeyref="PRODvars/PRODUCT_SP_ALTERNATIVE_NAME"
                    >OFFICIAL_PRODUCT_NAMEa</ph><?oxy_custom_end?> installer package.</cmd>
            </step>
        </steps>
    </taskbody>
</task>
